<%- include('../partials/header', {req: req}) %>

<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>About Stellar Simulations</h1>
    <p>Learn about our mission, our mobile simulator, and our team</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="about-intro section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="about-content">
      <div class="about-image animate-on-scroll">
        <img
          src="/images/about/trailer-exterior.jpg"
          alt="Stellar Simulations Mobile Trailer"
        />
      </div>
      <div class="about-text animate-on-scroll">
        <h2>Our Mission</h2>
        <p>
          At Stellar Simulations, we believe that space exploration is one of
          humanity's greatest adventures. Our mission is to bring the excitement
          and wonder of commanding a spaceship to people of all ages through our
          immersive bridge simulator experience.
        </p>
        <p>
          Founded by a team of space enthusiasts, engineers, and educators,
          we've created a unique mobile experience that combines cutting-edge
          technology with imaginative storytelling to deliver unforgettable
          adventures for birthday parties, corporate events, schools, and
          special occasions throughout Utah.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're passionate about inspiring the next generation of explorers
          while providing an experience that promotes teamwork, communication,
          and problem-solving skills in an exciting, engaging environment.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="simulator-details section bg-light">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-title">
      <h2>Our Mobile Bridge Simulator</h2>
      <p>
        Step aboard our custom-designed spaceship bridge and embark on an
        adventure
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="simulator-features">
      <div class="simulator-feature animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="simulator-feature-image">
          <img src="/images/about/bridge-interior.jpg" alt="Bridge Interior" />
        </div>
        <div class="simulator-feature-content">
          <h3>Immersive Environment</h3>
          <p>
            Our simulator is housed in a custom-built trailer that has been
            transformed into a realistic spaceship bridge. With ambient
            lighting, sound effects, and a panoramic main viewscreen, you'll
            feel like you're really traveling through space.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="simulator-feature animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="simulator-feature-content">
          <h3>Interactive Stations</h3>
          <p>
            The bridge features six crew stations, each with its own touchscreen
            interface and specialized controls. Stations include the Captain's
            Chair, Helm, Tactical, Science, Engineering, and Communications,
            allowing each crew member to play a vital role in the mission.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="simulator-feature-image">
          <img
            src="/images/about/crew-stations.jpg"
            alt="Interactive Crew Stations"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="simulator-feature animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="simulator-feature-image">
          <img src="/images/about/mission-control.jpg" alt="Mission Control" />
        </div>
        <div class="simulator-feature-content">
          <h3>Dynamic Missions</h3>
          <p>
            Our simulator features a variety of mission scenarios, from peaceful
            exploration to intense space battles. Each mission is guided by our
            experienced flight directors who adapt the story based on your
            crew's decisions, ensuring a unique experience every time.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="simulator-feature animate-on-scroll">
        <div class="simulator-feature-content">
          <h3>Mobile Experience</h3>
          <p>
            What makes Stellar Simulations special is that we bring the
            experience directly to you. Our self-contained trailer can be set up
            at almost any location in Utah, from driveways and parking lots to
            school grounds and event venues.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="simulator-feature-image">
          <img
            src="/images/about/trailer-setup.jpg"
            alt="Mobile Trailer Setup"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

